The evidence with the title 'How to spot a 'Free IPhone' or 'free ipad' scam - Macworld UK ' says Sep 12, 2018  ... The internet is awash with offers offree IPhones and free IPads .  ... And the offer itself is for the IPhone 6 rather than the 6s or 6s Plus.  ... If you see a free IPad offer on Facebook it is almost certainly ascam .  ... The original scam pretended to be from Apple ( note that Apple does n't ever give away its products). 
